nt applications in C/C++, C#, and Visual Basic .NET.

aders & libraries; Sample applications and source code; miscellaneous tools=
 and utilities. 

      This download does NOT include the DirectX 9.0 SDK =
Extras content, such as Japanese Docs, Symbol Files, Direct3D XFile Exporte=
rs, DirectShow DVD components, DirectPlay for PocketPC, and DirectMusic Pro=
ducer.
